Class CanonicalCodecFamilies

java.lang.Object
org.apache.commons.compress.harmony.pack200.CanonicalCodecFamilies
public class CanonicalCodecFamilies extends Object
Sets of codecs that share characteristics. Mainly used for different effort compression heuristics in BandSet.
